headline: Get Paid to Wait with Intel Stock (INTC) Put Options
summary: As investors surely already know, bellwether Intel Corp (INTC) has become the black sheep of the semiconductor family. Late to the game in shifting from CPUs to GPUs, Intel has lost industry leadership to Nvidia (NVDA) and long-term competitor Advanced Micro Devices (AMD). That fact is crystal clear when recognizing that NVDA stock’s market cap is now approximately 40x that of Intel.
